      <title>挪威今年或暂缓降息以冷却经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/norway-may-avoid-rate-cut-this-year-to-cool-resilient-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威央行表示，由于担心通胀将持续居高不下，今年剩余时间内可能需要将借贷成本维持在 2008 年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/norway-may-avoid-rate-cut-this-year-to-cool-resilient-economy</guid>
